1
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:42,440
Scheme.

2
00:01:16,320 --> 00:01:18,440
Open all the doors

3
00:01:18,440 --> 00:01:20,120
from the Yama Hall to the main hall.

4
00:01:20,120 --> 00:01:21,160
In two hours,

5
00:01:21,960 --> 00:01:23,120
I want everyone

6
00:01:23,120 --> 00:01:25,450
infected with the Skeleton Grass poison.

7
00:01:29,760 --> 00:01:31,039
Does this mean I didn't

8
00:01:31,039 --> 00:01:32,560
kill the Emperor myself?

9
00:01:33,520 --> 00:01:34,600
Are you satisfied?

10
00:01:35,360 --> 00:01:36,320
No,

11
00:01:36,440 --> 00:01:37,320
I beg you.

12
00:01:37,840 --> 00:01:39,120
Let me see my son one more time

13
00:01:39,120 --> 00:01:41,320
before I die.

14
00:01:41,720 --> 00:01:43,280
Why bother?

15
00:01:44,640 --> 00:01:46,500
He doesn't want to see you either.

16
00:01:46,520 --> 00:01:48,180
Besides, when my mother died,

17
00:01:48,920 --> 00:01:50,320
you didn't let me see her.

18
00:01:51,720 --> 00:01:52,840
But I'm merciful.

19
00:01:53,840 --> 00:01:55,520
You will be reunited soon.

20
00:01:59,440 --> 00:02:00,040
Men.

21
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:15,760
Mother, you sent someone so late to say you wanted to see me.

22
00:02:15,760 --> 00:02:17,220
What is the urgent matter?

23
00:02:18,040 --> 00:02:20,100
If it's still about the new policies,

24
00:02:20,400 --> 00:02:22,360
then I won't bother you with it.

25
00:02:23,520 --> 00:02:24,120
By the way,

26
00:02:24,760 --> 00:02:26,120
the recent uproar about

27
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:28,200
the King of Hell claiming lives,

28
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:30,200
how have you handled it, Mother?

29
00:02:33,320 --> 00:02:33,880
Mother!

30
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:36,560
Mother!

31
00:02:44,680 --> 00:02:46,560
Aren't you mourning for your father?

32
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:49,760
Why are you here at the Empress Dowager's place right now?

33
00:02:50,720 --> 00:02:52,280
Why can't I?

34
00:02:52,920 --> 00:02:54,320
After tonight,

35
00:02:54,640 --> 00:02:55,880
in this imperial palace,

36
00:02:55,880 --> 00:02:59,010
there won't be any place I cannot enter and leave at will.

37
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:04,040
The Princess has arrived!

38
00:03:08,040 --> 00:03:08,840
Your Majesty,

39
00:03:09,120 --> 00:03:10,280
Consort De has colluded with Prince Jia

40
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:10,880
to rebel.

41
00:03:12,800 --> 00:03:13,800
Princess Qingyi,

42
00:03:13,920 --> 00:03:15,180
do not speak nonsense.

43
00:03:15,560 --> 00:03:17,720
Your Majesty is so preoccupied with the new policies

44
00:03:17,720 --> 00:03:19,600
that you forgot what I look like.

45
00:03:19,920 --> 00:03:21,000
How would you know

46
00:03:21,160 --> 00:03:22,880
that your harem is in chaos?

47
00:03:30,520 --> 00:03:32,520
Following the late Emperor's edict,

48
00:03:32,520 --> 00:03:34,520
the great responsibility of the ancestral temple

49
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:36,800
is considered a noble duty.

50
00:03:37,040 --> 00:03:39,160
The current Emperor acts against the natural order

51
00:03:39,160 --> 00:03:40,200
and appoints treacherous officials,

52
00:03:40,200 --> 00:03:41,800
causing public outrage.

53
00:03:42,200 --> 00:03:43,840
The King of Hell has sent down a punishment

54
00:03:43,840 --> 00:03:45,000
as a warning,

55
00:03:45,400 --> 00:03:46,840
killing many palace servants.

56
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:48,000
Though I cannot bear it...

57
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:49,930
But for the great plan of the world,

58
00:03:50,560 --> 00:03:52,520
she perished together with the current Emperor.

59
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:54,040
State affairs are entrusted to King Jia.

60
00:03:54,040 --> 00:03:55,300
The Empress Dowager's

61
00:03:56,160 --> 00:03:57,040
last words.

62
00:04:02,720 --> 00:04:03,250
King Jia,

63
00:04:03,520 --> 00:04:06,120
is the Empress Dowager going to perish with me?

64
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:09,330
Do you take me for a three-year-old child?

65
00:04:10,160 --> 00:04:12,120
I thought your study of the new policies

66
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:13,720
had ruined your brain.

67
00:04:14,320 --> 00:04:15,800
In front of the edict,

68
00:04:16,240 --> 00:04:18,500
do you think they will believe your words

69
00:04:18,959 --> 00:04:20,690
or the words of the late Emperor

70
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:22,520
and the late Empress?

71
00:04:23,720 --> 00:04:25,440
What did you do to the Empress Dowager?

72
00:04:25,440 --> 00:04:26,320
If you dare

73
00:04:26,480 --> 00:04:27,800
to murder the Empress Dowager,

74
00:04:27,800 --> 00:04:29,330
I will tear you into pieces!

75
00:04:32,240 --> 00:04:34,640
You mother and son are really interesting.

76
00:04:35,120 --> 00:04:37,000
Didn't you usually fight fiercely?

77
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:39,330
Now you are sympathizing with each other.

78
00:04:39,800 --> 00:04:41,400
If you care about her so much,

79
00:04:42,120 --> 00:04:44,380
then go to the underworld to care for her.

80
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:47,360
Your Majesty,

81
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:49,000
he wants to forge

82
00:04:49,240 --> 00:04:51,040
the illusion that you and the Empress Dowager turned against each other because of the new policies

83
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:52,440
and perished together,

84
00:04:52,640 --> 00:04:53,159
so that

85
00:04:53,520 --> 00:04:55,780
he can succeed the throne legitimately.

86
00:04:57,240 --> 00:04:57,880
Yi'er,

87
00:04:59,320 --> 00:05:00,320
I didn't expect

88
00:05:00,840 --> 00:05:02,840
you would eventually betray me.

89
00:05:03,200 --> 00:05:04,040
Brother,

90
00:05:04,720 --> 00:05:05,780
did Mother's death

91
00:05:05,920 --> 00:05:07,560
fail to bring back your conscience?

92
00:05:07,560 --> 00:05:09,690
Are you going to keep making mistakes?

93
00:05:09,720 --> 00:05:10,680
I just want

94
00:05:11,800 --> 00:05:13,530
you to pay for my mother's life!

95
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:15,050
Stop talking nonsense.

96
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:18,160
Any more nonsense,

97
00:05:18,800 --> 00:05:20,460
and I won't let you off either.

98
00:05:22,600 --> 00:05:23,640
Let me tell you,

99
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:25,200
Liu Chuan is not dead.

100
00:05:26,080 --> 00:05:27,480
And he has already found

101
00:05:27,720 --> 00:05:29,780
the Yama Palace you carefully built.

102
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:31,120
Your plan

103
00:05:31,800 --> 00:05:33,040
will never succeed.

104
00:05:35,840 --> 00:05:36,960
Yama Palace.

105
00:05:37,840 --> 00:05:39,720
Can he still come back alive?

106
00:05:42,120 --> 00:05:43,960
It's not good to talk behind someone's back.

107
00:05:43,960 --> 00:05:44,680
King Jia.

108
00:05:51,960 --> 00:05:54,960
How come you didn't die after entering my Yama Palace?

109
00:05:55,280 --> 00:05:56,680
Where are my ghost soldiers?

110
00:05:56,680 --> 00:05:57,520
Come on.

111
00:05:57,560 --> 00:05:58,520
Ghost soldiers?

112
00:05:59,159 --> 00:06:00,280
Aren't they just some death row prisoners and suicide squad members

113
00:06:00,280 --> 00:06:02,440
controlled by your Skeleton Grass?

114
00:06:02,640 --> 00:06:04,300
I've already dealt with them.

115
00:06:08,720 --> 00:06:09,320
Hold this.

116
00:06:19,920 --> 00:06:21,520
Watch out for the grenade!

117
00:06:29,360 --> 00:06:33,520
Thank you, Mr. Liu.

118
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:34,440
You're welcome.

119
00:06:34,440 --> 00:06:36,640
Thank you.

120
00:06:38,400 --> 00:06:39,720
I know you have many people.

121
00:06:39,720 --> 00:06:40,760
For convenience,

122
00:06:40,960 --> 00:06:42,360
I made an antidote bomb.

123
00:06:42,760 --> 00:06:44,000
You are out of options, right?

124
00:06:44,000 --> 00:06:45,360
I'm so smart.

125
00:06:48,120 --> 00:06:48,680
Brother.

126
00:06:49,080 --> 00:06:50,940
Aren't you going to admit defeat?

127
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:52,330
Your Highness, save me!

128
00:06:53,159 --> 00:06:54,520
Can't you see it?

129
00:06:54,760 --> 00:06:55,560
This man,

130
00:06:55,640 --> 00:06:56,720
in order to achieve his goals,

131
00:06:56,720 --> 00:06:58,120
would sacrifice anyone,

132
00:06:58,159 --> 00:06:59,020
including you.

133
00:06:59,720 --> 00:07:00,520
Impossible.

134
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:01,720
Impossible.

135
00:07:01,720 --> 00:07:04,080
Your Highness, you said you'd make me your empress.

136
00:07:04,080 --> 00:07:04,680
Yes.

137
00:07:05,280 --> 00:07:07,740
Confer you the title of posthumous empress.

138
00:07:12,320 --> 00:07:13,320
Brother Liu,

139
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:16,160
you and I could have become sworn brothers,

140
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:17,520
become confidants,

141
00:07:19,360 --> 00:07:21,560
and share the world together.

142
00:07:22,920 --> 00:07:25,240
I'm a dignified junior coroner of Yingtian Prefecture.

143
00:07:25,240 --> 00:07:27,120
If my name is linked with a vicious prince like you,

144
00:07:27,120 --> 00:07:28,720
how can I face anyone in the future?

145
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:30,560
How can I build my personal brand?

146
00:07:30,560 --> 00:07:33,159
Then what's the difference between you and me?

147
00:07:33,520 --> 00:07:35,000
To lure me out,

148
00:07:35,360 --> 00:07:36,520
didn't you also sacrifice

149
00:07:36,520 --> 00:07:39,050
all those people on the Book of Life and Death?

150
00:07:41,240 --> 00:07:42,300
Speaking of which,

151
00:07:42,760 --> 00:07:44,960
I almost forgot if you hadn't mentioned it.

152
00:07:44,960 --> 00:07:45,820
Do you remember

153
00:07:45,960 --> 00:07:47,320
when you sent me to Lienv Cliff

154
00:07:47,320 --> 00:07:48,280
to sort out that

155
00:07:48,320 --> 00:07:49,980
human trafficking business?

156
00:07:51,520 --> 00:07:52,920
That suspended animation drug

157
00:07:52,920 --> 00:07:54,380
was made by you, wasn't it?

158
00:07:54,440 --> 00:07:55,640
I kept some of that drug

159
00:07:55,640 --> 00:07:56,840
and even improved it.

160
00:07:57,320 --> 00:07:58,600
After they were all poisoned,

161
00:07:58,600 --> 00:07:59,800
I put in the antidote.

162
00:08:00,320 --> 00:08:00,960
Although

163
00:08:01,320 --> 00:08:02,120
the medicinal properties

164
00:08:02,120 --> 00:08:02,850
and toxicity

165
00:08:02,920 --> 00:08:03,920
repel each other,

166
00:08:04,280 --> 00:08:05,560
it can still make people

167
00:08:05,560 --> 00:08:07,360
fall into a coma and feign death.

168
00:08:35,120 --> 00:08:36,240
Where am I?

169
00:08:36,400 --> 00:08:37,000
Eunuch,

170
00:08:37,400 --> 00:08:38,730
how are you feeling now?

171
00:08:38,919 --> 00:08:40,480
Still uncomfortable.

172
00:08:45,040 --> 00:08:45,920
Brother Liu.

173
00:08:47,120 --> 00:08:48,850
You live up to your reputation.

174
00:08:49,920 --> 00:08:51,760
Liu Chuan,

175
00:08:52,200 --> 00:08:53,660
you're really something.

176
00:08:55,120 --> 00:08:55,920
But listen,

177
00:08:57,720 --> 00:08:59,960
it's already a mess outside.

178
00:09:00,800 --> 00:09:02,840
Everyone in the world knows

179
00:09:02,920 --> 00:09:06,120
that the Emperor and the Empress Dowager don't get along.

180
00:09:06,320 --> 00:09:07,760
After tonight,

181
00:09:08,520 --> 00:09:10,720
the people will be plunged into misery.

182
00:09:11,040 --> 00:09:13,440
You will all be buried with me.

183
00:09:15,920 --> 00:09:16,980
Speaking of which,

184
00:09:17,320 --> 00:09:18,720
I've thought of that too.

185
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:20,520
Although I'm just a lowly coroner,

186
00:09:20,520 --> 00:09:22,380
I hate seeing people die the most.

187
00:09:22,520 --> 00:09:25,800
Thank you, Mr. Liu.

188
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:27,120
Is it over?

189
00:09:27,720 --> 00:09:28,560
Thank you.

190
00:09:36,160 --> 00:09:37,760
The Imperial Guard tally.

191
00:09:41,960 --> 00:09:43,000
Rest assured, Your Majesty.

192
00:09:43,000 --> 00:09:44,600
The Empress Dowager is fine.

193
00:10:09,120 --> 00:10:10,520
The Song Dynasty

194
00:10:11,240 --> 00:10:12,840
relies not only on Liu Chuan,

195
00:10:13,840 --> 00:10:15,040
but also on you.

196
00:10:34,320 --> 00:10:35,000
Prince Jia,

197
00:10:35,600 --> 00:10:37,040
you are out of options.

198
00:10:37,320 --> 00:10:38,240
Surrender.

199
00:10:39,320 --> 00:10:41,380
Since you are the late Emperor's son,

200
00:10:41,720 --> 00:10:43,380
I will leave your body intact.

201
00:10:51,560 --> 00:10:53,000
Leave my body intact?

202
00:11:02,720 --> 00:11:04,440
Leave my body intact?

203
00:11:09,120 --> 00:11:12,120
Everything in this world is always mine.

204
00:11:15,120 --> 00:11:18,400
You think everything ends with my death.

205
00:11:20,600 --> 00:11:22,200
No, no, no.

206
00:11:23,760 --> 00:11:25,800
No, no, no.

207
00:11:26,760 --> 00:11:29,040
The gates of hell have opened.

208
00:11:29,240 --> 00:11:32,200
The pen of the Book of Life and Death will never stop.

209
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:36,040
Liu Chuan.

210
00:11:36,680 --> 00:11:38,480
I will wait for you in hell.

211
00:11:41,960 --> 00:11:42,820
Your Highness.

212
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:46,860
Your Highness.

213
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:13,330
This is already the best way for him to die.

214
00:12:13,480 --> 00:12:14,040
Guards!

215
00:12:14,240 --> 00:12:14,800
Here.

216
00:12:16,800 --> 00:12:17,720
Take Consort De

217
00:12:18,520 --> 00:12:19,840
into custody and execute her.

218
00:12:19,840 --> 00:12:20,400
Yes.

219
00:12:21,120 --> 00:12:21,680
Move.

220
00:12:21,880 --> 00:12:22,440
Move.

221
00:12:31,360 --> 00:12:32,400
My dear Liu,

222
00:12:32,720 --> 00:12:33,320
you truly

223
00:12:33,560 --> 00:12:35,520
saved me from disaster.

224
00:12:35,600 --> 00:12:36,260
You are like

225
00:12:36,320 --> 00:12:38,050
a second brother Zhuoran to me.

226
00:12:38,520 --> 00:12:39,380
Please allow me

227
00:12:39,480 --> 00:12:40,200
to call you

228
00:12:40,480 --> 00:12:41,120
brother.

229
00:12:42,080 --> 00:12:44,320
Since the Emperor has said so,

230
00:12:44,320 --> 00:12:45,440
I will

231
00:12:45,760 --> 00:12:47,560
take Liu Chuan as my adopted son.

232
00:12:47,760 --> 00:12:49,220
So you two can be brothers.

233
00:12:50,600 --> 00:12:51,240
Mother,

234
00:12:51,720 --> 00:12:52,600
I...

235
00:13:10,520 --> 00:13:11,960
Cherish the little time

236
00:13:12,680 --> 00:13:14,160
you two have left.

237
00:13:26,920 --> 00:13:27,320
Hurry up.

238
00:13:27,320 --> 00:13:28,520
Get ready, everyone.

239
00:13:29,200 --> 00:13:29,920
Hurry.

240
00:13:29,920 --> 00:13:30,760
Don't dawdle.

241
00:13:30,760 --> 00:13:32,220
This red suits you so well.

242
00:13:32,520 --> 00:13:33,520
Be careful.

243
00:13:33,520 --> 00:13:35,780
You must be the most beautiful one today.

244
00:13:35,880 --> 00:13:37,280
Such an expensive thing.

245
00:13:38,280 --> 00:13:39,810
You are so beautiful today.

246
00:13:40,160 --> 00:13:41,400
It's so beautiful.

247
00:13:41,760 --> 00:13:43,720
What a perfect match.

248
00:13:43,720 --> 00:13:44,120
Indeed.

249
00:13:44,120 --> 00:13:46,120
What a couple.

250
00:13:46,720 --> 00:13:49,520
Do the Princess and the eldest lady of the Tu family

251
00:13:49,600 --> 00:13:51,480
want to steal my Liu?

252
00:13:51,480 --> 00:13:54,540
There's no hierarchy when it comes to stealing a groom.

253
00:13:55,600 --> 00:13:56,600
I am the Princess,

254
00:13:56,800 --> 00:13:58,320
so of course I have the final say.

255
00:13:58,320 --> 00:14:00,320
Qiuyue, I won't go easy on you today.

256
00:14:00,800 --> 00:14:01,920
As for you,

257
00:14:03,120 --> 00:14:04,580
don't even think about it.

258
00:14:07,600 --> 00:14:08,320
Liu Chuan,

259
00:14:08,320 --> 00:14:09,320
Liulang,

260
00:14:09,600 --> 00:14:10,200
Liu Chuan,

261
00:14:10,760 --> 00:14:11,520
Liu Chuan, you have to seek justice for me.

262
00:14:11,520 --> 00:14:12,040
Liulang.

263
00:14:12,040 --> 00:14:15,170
Lord Gu, the Chief Minister of Dali Temple, has arrived!

264
00:14:17,320 --> 00:14:18,450
By imperial decree,

265
00:14:25,960 --> 00:14:27,120
Liu Chuan is hereby appointed as

266
00:14:27,120 --> 00:14:28,520
Scholar of the Duanming Hall,

267
00:14:28,520 --> 00:14:30,320
and Hanlin Reader-in-Waiting.

268
00:14:30,720 --> 00:14:32,360
He shall oversee Jiangnan's criminal justice,

269
00:14:32,360 --> 00:14:33,720
hold the title of Supreme Pillar of State,

270
00:14:33,720 --> 00:14:35,720
and be ennobled as the Founding Marquis of Henei Commandery.

271
00:14:35,720 --> 00:14:37,240
He is granted the privilege of not being addressed by name during court audiences,

272
00:14:37,240 --> 00:14:39,400
and not having to hasten his steps when entering the court.

273
00:14:39,400 --> 00:14:41,160
Granted the authority to execute officials below the third rank

274
00:14:41,160 --> 00:14:42,220
before reporting.

275
00:14:43,040 --> 00:14:44,700
Bestowing the Imperial Sword

276
00:14:45,000 --> 00:14:46,560
and the military tally.

277
00:14:47,560 --> 00:14:48,960
Thank you, Your Majesty.

278
00:14:55,200 --> 00:14:57,280
Qiuyue is credited with protecting the Emperor,

279
00:14:57,280 --> 00:14:59,760
appointed as First-Class Imperial Bodyguard,

280
00:14:59,760 --> 00:15:01,480
and rewarded with a thousand pieces of gold.

281
00:15:01,480 --> 00:15:03,320
The Empress Dowager takes her as an adopted daughter.

282
00:15:03,320 --> 00:15:04,120
Bestowed the title of

283
00:15:04,120 --> 00:15:05,120
Princess Yiyong.

284
00:15:05,560 --> 00:15:06,360
End of decree.

285
00:15:06,720 --> 00:15:08,120
Thank you, Your Majesty.

286
00:15:13,080 --> 00:15:14,280
Congratulations, Martial Uncle.

287
00:15:14,280 --> 00:15:15,880
Congratulations, Martial Aunt.

288
00:15:15,880 --> 00:15:17,840
Congratulations to you, my dear nephew.

